description:
This is a 25 minute workout called '20 Minute Full Body Strength Workout (No Equipment/No Repeat)' from the channel Juice & Toya.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Progression Quest and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Tap in with us for a 20 minute FULL BODY strength building workout that requires no equipment! This workout focuses on 'time under tension'---meaning each exercises will be performed slow and controlled to ensure your muscles are fully engaged. This is a great workout for beginners who want to build good overall strength with basic bodyweight exercises. For the more advanced, feel free to add resistance using dumbbells, kettlebells, or weight vest to make it more challenging. Give the workout a go and let us know how you did in the comments! ðŸ”¥
